First thank you so much for your support. It helped us to navigate our first try at takeout only.
Today we will not be taking time slot orders. Sorry for the inconvenience but we might run out of certain items and don’t want to make it harder on you. When we close today we will reopen again June 4th with the full menu. And 7 days a week.
Again THANK YOU for your support and understanding. And remember you must have a mask on for on site ordering and social distancing. Please.

Patrice Popovic‎Smith's Clam Bar-Smitty's
May 21 at 10:59 AM ·

Noon-7pm. May 23-24-25

(Take out procedure)

We will be serving take out orders from a limited menu Saturday, Sunday and Monday from 12-7pm. We will only be taking orders by phone on credit cards (no cash). For the time being we will NOT be doing in person walk up orders. When you call your order in our staff will give you an estimated time to pick up. (20 minutes / 30 minutes etc.) When you arrive at the restaurant your order should be ready at our front counters with your name on the bag/bags. If your order isn’t at the counter when you get there, please try and wait in your car and check again in a couple minutes to keep in line with social distancing. Please wear a mask for our staff and others safety. Please do not wait on our benches! Strange time we know but hopefully it will not be for long. Thank you for your understanding.

Thank you everyone for your patience and support. We will be opening this Saturday, Sunday and Monday, May 23,24,25 with a limited menu and then closing until the first week in June. When we re-open, it will be with a full menu and 7 days a week. We will post the limited weekend menu this Thursday Thank you for your understanding.

We will only be doing take out, with phone orders only. No walk up ordering. We will post the pick up procedure on Thursday.

We are no longer old school. We now accept credit cards and have added 3 phone lines!

We know this has been a trying time for everyone and while this is our 47th summer it is certainly new and different. The clam bar has always been…
